home.title: Dimsum
home.des: Dimsum is a traditional Chinese dish, with a thin layer of dough on the outside and a filling inside: It can be salty or sweet, then fried, steamed, etc. Dimsum with the international transliteration is "thunder point", in Vietnamese it is read as dim sum, simply understood dim sum means a meal usually eaten in the morning.
